# DEPLOYMENT RULES - SERVER ONLY
# ============================================

## ALL development work MUST be done on the server
- Server: root@109.199.108.30
- Path: /BlueHub
- NEVER work on local (D:\BlueHub) for development

## When making any changes:
1. SSH to server: ssh root@109.199.108.30
2. cd /BlueHub
3. Edit files with: nano or cat > file << 'EOF'
4. Build: docker compose build admin --no-cache
5. Run: docker compose up -d admin
6. Test: curl http://localhost:3001
7. Check logs: docker logs bluehub-admin --tail 30

## IMPORTANT:
- No password needed (SSH key already set up)
- Always test after changes
- Report results after each step
- If you see errors, fix them and continue